data.description: Come check out this spacious , legal conforming  duplex on a double lot with plenty of parking space. Great investment opportunity!  Close to shopping, schools and train station. Both units are currently vacant.  First floor has 3 bedrooms , 1.5 baths and a sizeable enclosed porch. The Master bedroom  comes complete with  walk in closet and updated 1/2 bath.  Second floor has 3 bedrooms and one bath. Exterior was painted in 2021 and  interior of both units painted in 2023.  New Carpeting in both units 2023. First floor furnace installed in 2022 and second floor furnace installed in 2023. Water heater updated in 2019. Separate gas and electric meters for each unit.   Property is move in ready and being sold   AS-IS.
